        "Club career": "Moro was born in Abrera, Barcelona, Spain. He made his Serie A debut for Lazio on 20 July 2020 in a game against Juventus.On 23 August 2022, Moro joined Ternana on a season-long loan. In January 2023, Moro had his loan terminated and joined Real Oviedo on loan until the end of the season.On 17 July 2023, Moro moved to fellow Segunda División side Real Valladolid on a one-year loan deal. After helping in the club's promotion to La Liga, he signed a permanent four-year contract on 30 June 2024.",
